{{Han etym}}
Originally {{Han compound|丰|廾|c1=p|c2=s|t2=two hands|ls=psc|nocap=y}}， hence the original version is [[𠬻]]. {{zh-l|*手|hand}} was later added at the bottom, and the original character was corrupted into {{zh-l|*𡗗}}. Related to [[舉]].

